nodes.text: Star Wars: The Clone Wars: "Clone Commandos"

Star Wars: The Clone Wars: "Clone Commandos" is a second collection of the four episodes in Season One of Star Wars: The Clone Wars. It was released on September 15, 2009 and includes the following episodes: Rookies, Storm Over Ryloth, Innocents of Ryloth and Liberty on Ryloth, but with no extra bonus features or material.

In Storm Over Ryloth Ashley Eckstein, who plays Ahsoka, is credited as Ashley Drane. Although Eckstein is sometimes credited as Ashley Drane, in the Clone Wars series she has always been credited as Ashley Eckstein. Except in this one episode.
It was preceded in release by The Clone Wars: "A Galaxy Divided" and was followed by a box set of the entire first season on November 3, 2009.
